      <title>Besiege! Done with the current official content...</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/2015/02/08/besiege-is-still-in-alpha-and-most-of-the-maps-and-challenges-arent-ready-i-finished-up-what-there/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Feb 2015 04:53:12 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/2015/02/08/besiege-is-still-in-alpha-and-most-of-the-maps-and-challenges-arent-ready-i-finished-up-what-there/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Besiege! is still in alpha, and most of the maps and challenges aren&amp;rsquo;t ready. I finished up what there is of the main campaign &amp;ndash; the first island &amp;ndash; and had a lot of fun coming up with weird machines to bring the war home to these poor jumping people.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;ll pick it up again when the next island opens up.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://plus.google.com/s/%23Besiege&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;#Besiege&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  ﻿&lt;a href=&#34;https://plus.google.com/108460561201888322767/posts/DpMcmV6BkYL&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Besiege! Finishing off the first world.&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://plus.google.com/108460561201888322767/posts/DpMcmV6BkYL&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/yg69IIuKbCKgOImdRDNcmXzIjEQQmmq4ywZAMhZ2DgyTe-EpBkTJKPLNsEx4e7TvOE32I5hiCBluXe7fIzcmsQ=w506-h284-n&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;These are my solutions for the last few maps of the only currently officially shipped maps. There&amp;rsquo;s&lt;/p&gt;</description>
