      <description>&lt;p&gt;Silly, stupidly addictive game. Went back and tried to conquer a previous level with the power of flight. And a little later &amp;ndash; a mobile blender?  &lt;a href=&#34;https://plus.google.com/s/%23Besiege&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;#Besiege&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  ﻿&lt;a href=&#34;https://plus.google.com/108460561201888322767/posts/Kj6eRfd6pKB&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Yet more Besiege!&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://plus.google.com/108460561201888322767/posts/Kj6eRfd6pKB&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/proxy/plfQB5h-A3E1mJFekaM3E0xjmsP7UQ6gVas6EOXoTvyq5jQrJRJuBNRZSOMj3wpGy5GZVb6bdt4_nXvmhmvnpA=w506-h284-n&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A few more bespoke Besiege creations. Haven&amp;rsquo;t yet found the über siege weapon that will kill all th&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://plus.google.com/108460561201888322767/posts/Kj6eRfd6pKB&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;This was posted on Google+&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Besiege! Love at first siege...</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/2015/02/07/i-love-builder-games-like-minecraft-and-kerbal-space-program-when-i-saw-the-zany-creations-from-besiege/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 07 Feb 2015 02:40:33 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/2015/02/07/i-love-builder-games-like-minecraft-and-kerbal-space-program-when-i-saw-the-zany-creations-from-besiege/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I love &amp;ldquo;builder&amp;rdquo; games like Minecraft and Kerbal Space Program. When I saw the zany creations from Besiege (available from the developers &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.besiegethegame.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;http://www.besiegethegame.com/&lt;/a&gt;&#xA; or Steam Early Access) I knew I had to get it.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m pretty far from making the incredible creations I see everywhere&amp;hellip; but I have some ideas&amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://plus.google.com/s/%23Besiege&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;#Besiege&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  ﻿&lt;a href=&#34;https://plus.google.com/108460561201888322767/posts/REjd2c2BsB9&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Besiege Cannon Test&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://plus.google.com/108460561201888322767/posts/REjd2c2BsB9&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/zClYTrqPD5BVHtxmqkDs58jgTKk-ykYCFwmcAQZQ9Yopy6pLmr83OKAAQ5AJd1KrAw4fqqjj9crnff3XMTVWww=w506-h284-n&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Just playing around with one of the first levels of Besiege, where you build your own bizarre siege&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
